# Optional: Display power management
# Uncomment and modify the times below to automatically
# turn the display off and on at specific times
#
# DISPLAY_OFF=23:00
# DISPLAY_ON=07:00

# Notes:
# - Times are in 24-hour format (00:00 to 23:59)
